g.text: A separate DependentAPI resource is created
for each dependent API in the core function,
Register the availability of the downstraem API(s)
listen for new Service in state 'inactive'
Grant to a role on the downstraem API(s)
query for APIs matching declared dependencies using Component Client ID and secret
The component can query with a GET on the Canvas.Info service or register for callback notifications.
There could be more than 1 API available for a given dependency.
Call using Component Client ID and secret
